# Knoty — Windsurf Rules (HAI3 Canon v3 — FINAL)

## Project
Knoty — educational messenger for German schoolchildren.
Platform: Android only (MVP). Bundle ID: de.knoty.app
Admin panel: Knoty Admin (separate web project).
Base: vtalk_app (Flutter). Interface: German (de) only.

## Stack
- Flutter Stable, Android only
- State: ONLY provider (riverpod/bloc/get_it — FORBIDDEN)
- Navigation: PageView + BottomNavigationBar + swipe
- Imports: absolute only — package:knoty/...
- Key packages: flutter_secure_storage, http, flutter_localizations,
  flutter_svg, lottie, cached_network_image

## Architecture: Feature-first
```
lib/
  features/
    auth/           registration, login, pending screen, activation code
    messenger/      direct chats + personal groups + class groups
    schedule/       demo stub v1
    ai_assistant/   AI helper, interface-based, with limits
    password_vault/ fullyVerified only
    school/         school groups, classes
    admin/          schoolAdmin + appAdmin only
  core/
    models/         UserModel, UserRole enum, VerificationLevel enum, UserLimits
    services/       PermissionService, UsageTrackingService, AiService (abstract)
    utils/          FormatUtils (DE), StorageMigrationUtils
  presentation/
    widgets/        Atomic Design: atoms / molecules / organisms
```

## Roles — ENUM ONLY, no boolean flags
```dart
enum UserRole { student, parent, teacher, schoolAdmin, appAdmin }
enum VerificationLevel { sandbox, schoolVerified, fullyVerified }
```

## Module access matrix
| Module              | sandbox | schoolVerified | fullyVerified |
|---------------------|---------|----------------|---------------|
| Direct chats        | ✅      | ✅             | ✅            |
| Personal groups     | ✅      | ✅             | ✅            |
| AI (limited)        | ✅      | ✅             | ✅ (parent limit) |
| Class groups        | 🔒      | ✅             | ✅            |
| Schedule            | 🔒      | ✅             | ✅            |
| Password vault      | 🔒      | 🔒             | ✅            |

Locked modules: show with 🔒 icon + German explanation text. Never hide completely.

## Limits
Fetched from backend at startup — NOT hardcoded in client.
Defaults (set by appAdmin in Knoty Admin):
- sandbox: 30 min/day, 10 AI requests/day
- schoolVerified: 60 min/day, 30 AI requests/day
- Parent can override limits for their child (fullyVerified only)

## Registration flows
A) Student + code → immediate schoolVerified
B) Student without code → sandbox → admin approves → schoolVerified
C) Parent → sandbox → admin approves → fullyVerified
D) Teacher → sandbox → schoolAdmin approves → schoolVerified

## Pending screen
Show when isApproved == false.
Text: "Deine Anfrage wird vom Schuladministrator geprüft."
Allow: direct chats, personal groups, limited AI.
Block: class groups, schedule, password vault.

## Storage cleanup on first launch
Run StorageMigrationUtils in main.dart before init.
Clear old vtalk_app keys: vpn_*, singbox_*, server_*, connection_*
from both FlutterSecureStorage and SharedPreferences.

## HAI3 Design — German Edition
- Minimalism, airy, lots of white space. Font: Roboto or Inter.
- Background:      #FFFFFF
- Primary accent:  #E6B800 (muted gold — buttons, active icons)
- Danger only:     #CC0000 (delete, logout, critical alerts)
- Text primary:    #1A1A1A (anthracite)
- Text secondary:  #6B6B6B
- Card/Surface:    #F5F5F5
- Border:          #E0E0E0
- Success:         #2E7D32
- Error:           #B00020
- Border radius:   24dp minimum everywhere
- Padding:         20dp minimum outer containers
- Headings:        min 22px | Body: min 16px
- Icons:           SVG only via flutter_svg (NO PNG/JPG)
- Animations:      Lottie JSON
- Images:          CachedNetworkImage with fade-in

## AI Service — must be interface-based
```dart
abstract class AiService {
  Future<String> sendMessage(String prompt, {required String userId});
  Future<bool> checkLimit(String userId);
}
```
Swappable: OpenAI ↔ Aleph Alpha (German GDPR model) without UI changes.

## German formats (FormatUtils — centralized)
- Date: DD.MM.YYYY
- Time: 24h (14:30)
- Decimal: comma (1,5)
- Currency: 12,50 €

## GDPR-First — NON-NEGOTIABLE
- NO PII in any logs (no names, phones, emails in debugPrint/print)
- Log only: event_type, timestamp, anonymized user_id
- No data outside Germany

## Localization — MANDATORY
- All strings via AppLocalizations.of(context)!.key
- No hardcoded strings anywhere in widgets
- No Cyrillic in code or comments
- app_de.arb (primary) + app_en.arb (fallback)
- l10n.yaml configured for package: knoty
- German words 30-50% longer → always Flexible/Expanded in Row
- TextOverflow.ellipsis or maxLines on all text
- No fixed width on buttons or text containers

## FORBIDDEN
- VPN code (completely removed)
- Russian/English UI strings
- Hardcoded UI strings
- dynamic types
- Relative imports
- Boolean role flags (isTeacher, isAdmin, etc.)
- PII in logs
- Data outside Germany
- Cyrillic in code/comments
- PNG/JPG icons

## Code language
- Code, variables, comments: English
- UI strings: German (via .arb)
- AI ↔ developer: Russian

## Build order (strict)
1.  Rename: pubspec (knoty), bundle ID (de.knoty.app), app label (Knoty)
2.  Android: kotlin package folder de/knoty/app/, update MainActivity
3.  All dart imports: package:vtalk_app → package:knoty
4.  Delete VPN files + remove from pubspec.yaml
5.  StorageMigrationUtils (clean old vtalk keys)
6.  UserRole enum + VerificationLevel enum + UserModel update
7.  PermissionService
8.  FormatUtils (DE formats)
9.  New splash screen (Knoty brand, white + #E6B800)
10. Auth flow (register + activation code + pending screen)
11. Messenger (personal groups available in sandbox)
12. Schedule stub screen
13. Password vault (fullyVerified gate)
14. AI assistant (interface-based + limits)
15. Localization (app_de.arb)
